UID:coptic2026-89@coptic-calendar.app
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20261026
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20261027
SUMMARY:St. John Chrysostom (16 Paope)
DESCRIPTION:16 Paope 1743 AM - 'Golden-mouthed' preacher. Archbishop of Constantinople. One of the greatest Church Fathers.
